  27 Jul 2005; Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org>
  libdvb-0.5.0-r1.ebuild, libdvb-0.5.5.ebuild:
  Stable on PowerPC, dependency for MythTV

*libdvb-0.5.5 (30 Jan 2005)

  30 Jan 2005; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org> +files/errno.patch,
  -libdvb-0.2.1.ebuild, -libdvb-0.2.3.ebuild, libdvb-0.5.0-r1.ebuild,
  libdvb-0.5.5.ebuild:
  old version clean out and errno.patch added as per bug #75471. Thanks to
  Konstantin Münning <konstantin@muenning.com>

  06 Dec 2004; Thomas Raschbacher <lordvan@gentoo.org> :
  Version bump; fixes Bug #41060
  Changed patch to work with 0.5.5, it renames the dia script to dia_dvb now

  07 Jun 2004; Travis Tilley <lv@gentoo.org> libdvb-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  stable on amd64

  27 Apr 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> libdvb-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add inherit eutils

  26 Mar 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> libdvb-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

  08 Mar 2004; Jon Portnoy <avenj@gentoo.org> libdvb-0.5.0-r1.ebuild :
  AMD64 keywords.

  17 Feb 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> libdvb-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  add ~alpha and ~ia64

*libdvb-0.5.0-r1 (19 Oct 2003)

  19 Oct 2003; Max Kalika <max@gentoo.org> libdvb-0.5.0-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml, files/libdvb-0.5.0-gentoo.patch:
  Bring the 0.5.0 version to media-libs. Ditch DVB.cc patch as it has been fixed
  upstream. Consolidate the other two patches into one and use epatch. Properly
  install sample_progs and samplerc items. Fixes bug 30676.

*libdvb-0.5.0 ( 04 Oct 2003)
  04 Oct 2003; Thomas Raschbacher <lordvan@gentoo.org>: libdvb-0.5.0.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  This includes dvb-mpegtools (see description) initial ebuild

*libdvb-0.2.3 (21 Mar 2003)

  21 Mar 2003; Martin Holzer <mholzer@gentoo.org> libdvb-0.2.1.ebuild,
  libdvb-0.2.3.ebuild:
  moved media-video to media-libs

*media-video/libdvb-0.2.3 (21 Mar 2003)
